===Adjective===
'''甘い''' ([[あまい]], [[amai]])
:甘い ''(''[[うまい]]'', [[umai]])''
# Tasting like sugar or honey: [[sweet]]. 
# Lacking saltiness.
# Fragrance or atmosphere that is reminiscent of the taste of honey.
# Having characteristic of something that lures people's hearts and misleads.
# Lacking discipline. To lack strictness or accurateness.
# An unsatisfactory or incomplete state.
# A weak intensity.

